@end smallexample

@c Another alternative of overriding those setting is to  set
@c @enindex R_JAVA_LD_LIBRARY_PATH
@c @env{R_JAVA_LD_LIBRARY_PATH} (e.g.@: in @file{~/.Renviron}), or use
