@c be negative), and the default is not to search for a suitable LAPACK
@c library, and this is definitely @strong{not} recommended.  You can
@c specify a specific LAPACK library or a search for a generic library by
@c the configuration option @option{--with-lapack}.  The default for
@c @option{--with-lapack} is to check the @acronym{BLAS} library and then
@c look for an external library @samp{-llapack}.  Sites searching for the
